title: Yet Another Bouldering Film.divx (Climbing)
description:
Originally ULd by ffast - compressed with Dr. DivX - sound works now! Description below is copied from the original post by ffast:

My first attempt to create a climbing movie (and boy you can see that from filming and editing!).

Includes climbing in Switzerland (Magic Wood) and Finland (Vaasa, Rovaniemi, Oulu).

BTW, you can freely skip the Oulu part, because it\&#039;s scrambling on some 6a problems.
